434
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:48,673
The cut off head?

435
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,559
I... i...
In the well! In the well!

436
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:56,032
I will go check.

437
00:34:57,680 --> 00:35:01,389
You can walk? - When you
are here, I feel better.

438
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:03,995
Just leave it to me.

