588
00:55:18,760 --> 00:55:21,718
Wait. I'll call them.

589
00:55:33,680 --> 00:55:37,229
<i>Help, please help me!</i>
<i>I beg you!</i>

590
00:55:37,680 --> 00:55:39,238
