We simply ask her, how to
open the door! - Exactly!

629
00:59:37,520 --> 00:59:38,555
Auntie?

630
00:59:38,960 --> 00:59:41,155
Auntie!
- Auntie?

631
00:59:42,640 --> 00:59:45,598
