No!

638
01:00:08,720 --> 01:00:11,314
I'm afraid!
- Please!

639
01:00:11,760 --> 01:00:17,676
Yes, that's a good idea! - That b
to the g simply strengthens me!

640
01:00:35,560 --> 01:00:36,754
Shouldn't Oshare slowly

641
01:00:37,640 --> 01:00:38,914
be coming back?

